content.title: Find and update company information - GOV.UK
content.metaDescription: Free company information from Companies House including registered office address, filing history, accounts, annual return, officers, charges, business activity
content.content:
[Companies House does not verify the accuracy of the information filed(link opens a new window)](http://resources.companieshouse.gov.uk/serviceInformation.shtml#compInfo)     
 
- [Sign in / Register](/signin)
 
    **For Information:** [UK company law is changing](https://changestoUKcompanylaw.campaign.gov.uk).   
#  Search the register 
 Enter company name, number or officer name
    Search     [Advanced company searchLink opens in new window](/advanced-search)   
## Current features include
 
 
- [File abridged or full accounts](/accounts/guidance)New
 
- Change a registered office address
 
- View company data and document images
 
- Search for disqualified directors
 
- Order certificates and certified documentsNew
 
- Follow companies
 
   
## Planned features
 
 
- [Other document filings](/help/other-filings)
 
   
## Other useful tools
 
 
- [Company name availability checkerLink opens in new window](/company-name-availability)
 
- [Alphabetical company searchLink opens in new window](/alphabetical-search)New
 
- [Dissolved company searchLink opens in new window](/dissolved-search)New
